description.fr:
Lorsqu'elle subit des dégâts\_: {ATvalue:at,percent,+}.
\---
{%attack} Les dégâts se propagent d'adversaire en adversaire autour\_<sprite name="cell_around"> de la cible.
\---
Invoque un {Summoning:1133} autour\_<sprite name="cell_around"> de chaque adversaire touché.
description.en:
On taking damage: {ATvalue:at,percent,+}.
\---
{%attack} The damage spreads from opponent to opponent around\_<sprite name="cell_around"> the target.
\---
Summons one {Summoning:1133} around\_<sprite name="cell_around"> each opponent hit.
description.es:
Cuando sufre daños: {ATvalue:at,percent,+}.
\---
{%attack} Los daños se propagan de adversario en adversario alrededor\_<sprite name="cell_around"> del objetivo.
\---
Invoca un {Summoning:1133} alrededor\_<sprite name="cell_around"> de cada adversario alcanzado.
description.de:
Wenn sie Schaden erleidet: {ATvalue:at,percent,+}.
\---
{%attack} Der Schaden springt im Umkreis\_<sprite name="cell_around"> des Ziels von Gegner zu Gegner über.
\---
Beschwört einen {Summoning:1133} im Umkreis\_<sprite name="cell_around"> von jedem getroffenen Gegner.
description.pt:
Quando ela sofre danos: {ATvalue:at,percent,+}.
\---
{%attack} Se propagam de adversário em adversário em\_volta\_<sprite name="cell_around"> do alvo.
\---
Invoca um {Summoning:1133} em\_volta\_<sprite name="cell_around"> de cada adversário atingido.
